room_title: Escape room "44 Winter Wood Lane" by Mass Escape in New Bedford
room_description: You have received a letter that your estranged great aunt has passed away. You had lost touch with her ever since her daughter died very suddenly, years ago. It turns out that you were her last remaining relative and she has left her house and all its possessions in your name. Whatever did happen to her daughter? And what did your aunt leave for you? You must meet the caretaker to view the house to claim your inheritance!
